            <li><button class="btn btn-dark btn-lg"  id="btn1">Monogatari</button></li>
            <div class="inf" id="inf1"><p>The story is about Koyomi Araragi, a former vampire and high school student. One day, while walking down the stairs at school, his shy but beautiful classmate Hitagi Senjogahara fell on him from somewhere above. Koyomi, instinctively tensed up, prepared to take the considerable weight in his arms, and was surprised to find that the girl, in violation of all the laws of physics is almost weightless. He soon became acquainted with Hitaga's abrupt temper, who did not want her strange secret to be known to anyone. Despite insults and threats from her, Koyomi introduces her to his friend, Mame Oshino, who not long ago helped him transform from a vampire back into a human.
                </p>
